		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Tag <code>T2B</code>: Evolution</h1>
		Language evolution, co-evolution, maintenance, migration. Work about software language change and its consequences: language evolution, coupled/co-evolution of languages with tools or language definitions with language instances, migrations, refactorings across versions, maintenance techniques for language ecosystems. Process aspects often get secondary <a href="t2a.html">T2A</a>, tracking changes by linking related artefacts can be secondary <a href="t5g.html">T5G</a>.
